data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom Cape Cod style home in the heart of Portsmouth. This cozy residence features a spacious kitchen, welcoming living room, and lovely backyard. Recently renovated in 2022, including a new roof, kitchen with granite countertops, updated baths, ceramic tile, laminate flooring, and fresh paint throughout. Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and entertainment venues, offering the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility. Some photos are virtually staged.
